window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Three lifelong best friends go to a destination wedding...and nothing will ever be the same.</b></p> <p><i>From USA Today and #1 Amazon bestselling author Pippa Grant comes the series box set of the chart-topping Three BFFs and a Wedding trilogy, plus a full-length bonus novel set adjacent to the Three BFFs world.</i> </p> <p><b>The Worst Wedding Date</b>, <i>a #1 Amazon bestseller,</i> is a frolicking good time of a destination wedding enemies-to-lovers romcom, complete with a good girl bridesmaid, her best friend’s brother, so many secrets, kittens, chocolate chip cookies, and more than one hitch on the way to happily ever after.</p> <p><b>The Gossip and the Grump</b>, <i>a #3 Amazon bestseller</i>, is a one night stand to enemies-to-lovers romcom featuring a woman desperately trying to unlearn everything she knows about everyone, a grumpy hero hiding a secret heart of gold, an unfortunate incident with powdered cheese, and the world’s biggest lap puppy.</p> <p><b>The Bride's Runaway Billionaire</b>, <i>a #1 Amazon bestseller</i>, is a swoony solo honeymoon romcom featuring a runaway bride who's accidentally gone viral, a happy-go-lucky celebrity about to have his world turned upside down by a vacation fling, an accidental secret baby, and a chicken with an attitude.</p> <p><b>The Last Eligible Billionaire</b>, <i>a #1 Amazon bestseller</i>, is a grumpy-sunshine fake dating romance featuring a botched wax job, a newly-single woman in over her head, a billionaire in over his heart, and the sweetest misguided dog to ever play matchmaker…or at least make sure these two anti-love birds never have clothes when they get out of the shower. <i>This bonus full-length romance is presented first in the box set for optimal reading experience.</i></p> <p>Tropes: grumpy sunshine, enemies to lovers, brother's best friend, billionaire, celebrity, fake dating, boss-employee, small town</p>"; 
